{"tid":273432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"橋本環奈公開直播人生最短的一次　網友「我跟媽媽介紹妳了。」","createTime":"2017-06-06T14:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T09:11:32.000Z","uid":9573,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c870d5e9258e23234b1952769044ea631089113b","tid":273432,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2573/d2573733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2573%2Fd2573733.jpg&h=e4ff2932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈直播中公開剪短髮。<br />\n<br />\n日本女星橋本環奈剪短髮了！她6日在直播中公開剪掉招牌長髮，同時宣傳主演的夏季日劇《警視廳生物係》，短短40分中內就剪掉一半到肩膀，吸引4萬5千網友同步觀看，超過200萬人按讚，還湧入4萬則留言狂讚「天使啊。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2573/d2573732.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2573%2Fd2573732.jpg&h=285529ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈一邊剪髮一邊讀網友留言，看到訊息太長靠近鏡頭，表情超萌。<br />\n<br />\n橋本環奈一邊剪髮，一邊在直播中談近況。她近日跟風推特熱門話題「跟女友約會中」，上傳一張搭公車的自拍照，綁雙馬尾加上圍圍巾，臥蠶大眼加上甜笑入鏡，還PO文「可以當作女友約會照哦。」這張「男友視角」的美照掀起網路轟動，大批粉絲留言搶認男友，眾人紛紛幻想說「妳圍了我送的圍巾」、「妳每次都搶著坐我後面」、「我跟媽媽介紹妳了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vklu5m2r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvklu5m2r&h=c1779d05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈上傳自拍照，留言「可以當作跟女友約會中用」，激起大批網友搶當男友。<br />\n<br />\n直播時間將近49分鐘，橋本環奈全程保持燦爛笑容，自己當主持人和網友互動，一邊聊新日劇的內容，一邊回答網友問題。不知不覺中她的頭髮就被剪掉一大半，還大玩手機的美拍APP，2位髮型師幫忙吹頭、捲髮，雖然曾為電影《水手服與機關槍》曾剪短髮，這次再剪短表示：「這是我人生中最短的一次。」全新髮型呈現在網友面前，令大家超級興奮激讚「簡直像看斷髮儀式」、「好適合」、「整個人都變了」、「還是好可愛啊！」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2573/d2573735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2573%2Fd2573735.jpg&h=229020b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈自己當主持人，直播將近49分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2573/d2573734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2573%2Fd2573734.jpg&h=ee3a202b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈短髮新造型：「人生中最短的一次。」"},{"pid":"8abef05a019d0b185b09972e580ed3cd91ea2f45","tid":273432,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"99.9%"},{"pid":"270624f472add122c96a1f34b0bbd1090b12a75c","tid":273432,"uid":55420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:17:44.000Z","msg":"頂明明之前入親依啲post都好警惕，係今次唔記得睇咗名先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85a6ba4edc035906d3cd87f5fee57aa1c4c2105","tid":273432,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頂明明之前入親依啲post都好警惕，係今次唔記得睇咗名先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有睇名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae804e867b7c36f429a303d70c0a85119109dd2e","tid":273432,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:19:21.000Z","msg":"都係長髮正啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad364d623021881d4a6de691e4e6a19b160688a","tid":273432,"uid":46737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"植入式千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c7121ab38f27ef575a723fdb073fd21b326d11","tid":273432,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>植入式千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇睇名入 拉到落去諗緊點解差咁遠 望真d先知千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da8b31bc116bde0cdf798f1459c708f83ec3e56","tid":273432,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:29:48.000Z","msg":"唔睇留言都唔知有千雪<img src=\"/assets/f